  <brief_title>Study on Enzalutamide and Flutamide in Patients With Castration Resistant Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase IV Study Comparing Enzalutamide Versus Flutamide in CRPC Patients Who Have Failed Combined Androgen Blockade Therapy With Bicalutamide Plus ADT</official_title>
